content.p: Tan Jing Shen is an undergraduate studying Applied Psychology and Management Studies. He talks about his interests, why he chose to study with Nottingham and what he likes best about his course. Caroline Ndalama is a postgraduate student in Management Psychology. She talks about the benefits of her course and the knowledge that she is looking forward to taking back home. telephone: +6 (03) 8924 8693 fax: +6 (03) 8924 8020
